andes of the particles is not equal to 0\nand if\nplayer was on floor\nor player is jumping from the wall\nor player has just jumped from a wall\nor player was dashing (variable is true)\nor player was dead (variable is true)\nor the player was not against a wall and was not climbing (variable is false)\nor the player was climbing (variable is true) and was not pressing down\nthen we set the particles capacity to 0 (this will remove the particles smoothly, rather than deleting the particles immediatly, we set its capacity to 0, so it stops spawning particles and auto delete it self when its out of particles)"},{"type":"BuiltinCommonInstructions::Standard","conditions":[{"type":{"inverted":true,"value":"BuiltinCommonInstructions::CompareNumbers"},"parameters":["SlidingParticles.Tank()","=","0"]},{"type":{"inverted":true,"value":"PickedInstancesCount"},"parameters":["SlidingParticles","=","0"]},{"type":{"value":"BuiltinCommonInstructions::Or"},"parameters":[],"subInstructions":[{"type":{"value":"PlatformBehavior::IsOnFloor"},"parameters":["PlayerHitbox","PlatformerObject"]},{"type":{"value":"BooleanVariable"},"parameters":["IsJumpingFromWallToAnother","True",""]},{"type":{"value":"AdvancedJump::WallJump::HasJustWallJumped"},"parameters":["PlayerHitbox","WallJump",""]},{"type":{"value":"BooleanObjectVariable"},"parameters":["PlayerHitbox","IsDashing","True",""]},{"type":{"value":"BooleanObjectVariable"},"parameters":["PlayerHitbox","IsDead","True",""]},{"type":{"value":"BuiltinCommonInstructions::And"},"parameters":[],"subInstructions":[{"type":{"inverted":true,"value":"AdvancedJump::WallJump::IsAgaintWall"},"parameters":["PlayerHitbox","WallJump",""]},{"type":{"value":"BooleanObjectVariable"},"parameters":["PlayerHitbox","IsClimbing","False",""]}]},{"type":{"value":"BuiltinCommonInstructions::And"},"parameters":[],"subInstructions":[{"type":{"value":"BooleanObjectVariable"},"parameters":["PlayerHitbox","IsClimbing","True",""]},{"type":{"inverted":true,"value":"KeyFrom