player but at the bottom (floor) (so we checked if there is no wall on the right side of the player at his center Y but there is a wall on the player feet on the right side)\nthen we set the player variable ClimbingOnLedge to true\nand we remove the timer (used in climbing events above to update the player falling speed)\nthen we reset the player max falling speed back to 400 (default)\nand we set the climbing variable to false (means the paleyr is not climbing anymore)\nand we set the climb variable to true (means plyer can press climb button)\nthen we add force to the -35 angle (Top Right) at 200 length (speed)\nthen we wait 0.12 (till the player has finished auto climbing)\nthen we set the climbing on ledge variable to false (means the player has finished climbing on ledge)\nthen we stop the force on the player (we started in the force action above it)\nthen we enable the WallJump behaviour again"},{"type":"BuiltinCommonInstructions::Standard","conditions":[{"type":{"inverted":true,"value":"FlippableCapability::FlippableBehavior::FlippedX"},"parameters":["PlayerSkin","Flippable"]},{"type":{"value":"BuiltinCommonInstructions::Not"},"parameters":[],"subInstructions":[{"type":{"value":"Raycast"},"parameters":["AllLevelsCollisions","PlayerHitbox.CenterX()","PlayerHitbox.CenterY()+10","0","12","","",""]}]},{"type":{"value":"Raycast"},"parameters":["AllLevelsCollisions","PlayerHitbox.CenterX()","PlayerHitbox.BoundingBoxBottom()","0","12","","",""]}],"actions":[{"type":{"value":"SetBooleanObjectVariable"},"parameters":["PlayerHitbox","ClimbingOnLedge","True",""]},{"type":{"value":"RemoveTimer"},"parameters":["","\"StopPlayerFallingSpeed\""]},{"type":{"value":"PlatformBehavior::MaxFallingSpeed"},"parameters":["PlayerHitbox","PlatformerObject","=","400",""]},{"type":{"value":"SetBooleanObjectVariable"},"parameters":["PlayerHitbox","IsClimbing","False",""]},{"type":{"value":"SetBooleanVariable"},"parameters":["CantPressClimbKey","True",""]},{"type":{"value":"AddForceAL"},"